overview: As the King of Trios tournament heats up, the Rey de Voladores begins and Amasis, Matt Cross, Flip Kendrick, Malachi Jackson, Frightmare, Ophidian, Cheech, and Rich Swann are set for high-flying action! Night 2 also features non-tournament bouts: Brodie Lee fights former partner Grizzly Redwood, then Christopher Daniels wrestles Hallowicked!
title: CHIKARA King of Trios 2010 - Night 2
